Package com.pytsoft.cachelock.connector

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CacheClient
    The CacheClient interface defines the required commands for cache client to implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MemcachedClient
    The MemcachedClient class is the Memcached client implementation of CacheClient with usage of spymemcached library.
    RedisClient
    The RedisClient class is the Redis client implementation of CacheClient with usage of Jedis library.
    RedisClusterClient
    The RedisClusterClient class is the Redis-cluster client implementation of CacheClient with usage of Jedis library.
